 -- Function: wint_t putwchar (wchar_t WC)
     Preliminary: | MT-Safe | AS-Unsafe corrupt | AC-Unsafe corrupt lock
     | *Note POSIX Safety Concepts::.

     The `putwchar' function is equivalent to `putwc' with `stdout' as
